## Scenario 2: LogTransaction

First create AuditLog table.

```sql
CREATE TABLE AuditLog(

LogID NUMBER GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY,

TransactionID NUMBER,

ActionDate DATE,

Description VARCHAR2(100)

);
```

Trigger:

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER LogTransaction

AFTER INSERT
ON Transactions

FOR EACH ROW

BEGIN

INSERT INTO AuditLog(

TransactionID,
ActionDate,
Description

)

VALUES(

:NEW.TransactionID,
SYSDATE,
'Transaction Added'

);

END;
/
```

